  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Through long and intensive training you mastered Burglary. Few people in this world can match your capabilities in this area.</p><p>Gain the following master feats: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.7GmXKrkzmInkFyEr]{Quick Unlock}.</p><p><strong>Skill Potency</strong></p><p>At 9th level, you gain a +2 item bonus to Thievery checks involving @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.2EE4aF4SZpYf0R6H]{Pick a Lock}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.cYdz2grcOcRt4jk6]{Disable a Device}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.ijZ0DDFpMkWqaShd]{Palm an Object}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.RDXXE7wMrSPCLv5k]{Steal}. At 17th level, if you have @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.IZbjUaZI5zHTd1Vp]{Legendary Thief}, this bonus increases to +3.</p>",
